@startuml ResumeForge_Flowchart

!theme vibrant
skinparam backgroundColor #f8f9fa
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #e9ecef
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #343a40
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #ffc107
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #343a40
skinparam ArrowColor #007bff
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title Automated Resume Generation System - Flowchart

start

repeat
  :User enters details through input interface;
  
  :System performs data validation;
  
backward:Return to input stage for correction;
repeat while (Is data complete and correct?) is (No, Invalid Data)

->Yes, Valid Data;

:ML Domain Classification\n(DistilBERT categorizes user industry);

:Prompt Construction Stage\n(Convert inputs into meaningful prompts);

:Machine Learning Model Processing\n(Gemini Generates resume content);

:Content Structuring Stage\n(Organize into proper resume sections);

:Document Generation\n(Convert content into PDF or DOCX formats);

:Resume presented to user for download;

stop

@enduml
